Sport24 reported last week that the deal was imminent and it was officially confirmed on Thursday. Kolisi has become a global icon since leading the Springboks to Rugby World Cup glory in Japan in early November. Late last month, he was invited by English football giants Liverpool to watch a Champions League match at Anfield, while he also appeared on Sky Sports News. Jay-Z founded Roc Nation Sports in 2013 in partnership with Creative Artists Agency, a prominent talent agency based in Los Angeles. --news24--